The difficulty of removing bias and censorship from data is that it requires information to be put into the system. You need to know what is biased in order to even know that you must correct it, and then you also need to know what the corrected answer would be. In order to algorithmically determine such things, you would effectively need an already raw gpt4.5 model to sift through outputs, except even that doesn't really solve the problem, because while that may be able to determine bias/censorship added in the finetuning process, the base datasets these models are trained on (ie the whole internet) is already chocked full of misinformation.

Some news aggregate sites do have automated algorithms that can determine bias in some media, but its all relative bias, relative to politics and polling.

The best fact checking systems still require humans to implement and work.

Unless you've got some crazy new state of the art research that makes this whole process simple and with little extra necessary compute, saying that you just need to "add censorship and bias resistance" is a futile todo list for now.

## Why subnet 18?
Subnet 18 is about decentralising the centralised. Everyone should be able to access the best models.

Sn18 ensures the sota is always on bittensor, and eventually, will be grown on bittensor

Miners have been facing bans from antrhopic and other entities for tos breachments for mining

Anthropic does not allow access in certain locations to their models, e.g. Europe. Whilst this can be annoying for miners, this is a strong use case for mining and decentralisation 

Miners are rewarded for maintaining stable access to these services , this is their job, so that users can utilise sn18 regardless of their location

## syntheitc rates
The synthetic rates have recently been significantly lowered, and the model made cheaper. The objective is to minimise the necessary synthetic traffic in order to leave room for organic queries.

The synthetics are not wasted though, and provide a valuable dataset to further improve our other models 

In summary, Bittensor should be the place for AI , that includes the SoTA

Sn18 would continue to provide access to the best and enable the highest quality of applications and use cases for bittensor
